                        <hi rendition="#u">Raffles</hi></persName> and the Illustrious <persName key="H0013277"><hi rendition="#u">Cuvier</hi></persName>, respecting the
                    <lb/>zoological collections sent home by my Friend from whom I had <lb/>a letter
